Action: An error occurred while creating the backup.
An error occurred while writing to the backup file "%s".
Are you sure you want to delete the selected backup(s)?
Handling: Er du sikker på at du vil slette de valgte backups?

Action: Backup file "%s" cannot be read from or written to.
Handling: Backupfilen "%s" kan ikke læses eller skrives.
Backup file handler er ikke angivet.

Action: Backup file path was not specified.
Handling: Stien til backupfilen er ikke angivet.

Action: Failed to delete one or several backups.
Handling: Kunne ikke slette en eller flere backups.

Action: Not enough free space to create backup.
Handling: Ikke tilstrækkelig ledig plads til at tage backup.

Action: Not enough permissions to create backup.
Handling: Ikke tilstrækkelige tilladelser til at tage backup.

Action: Not enough permissions to perform rollback
Handling: Ikke tilstrækkelige tilladelser til at udføre rollback

Action: Please either unselect the "Put store on the maintenance mode" checkbox or update your permissions to proceed with the backup."
Handling: Du skal enten undlade at vælge "Sæt forretning i vedligeholdelsestilstand" eller opdatere dine tilladelser for at fortsætte med backup."

Action: Please either unselect the "Put store on the maintenance mode" checkbox or update your permissions to proceed with the rollback."
Handling: Du skal enten undlade at vælge "Sæt forretning i vedligeholdelsestilstand" eller opdatere dine tilladelser for at fortsætte med rollback."

Action: Put store on the maintenance mode while backup's creation
Handling: Sæt forretning i vedligeholdelsestilstand mens der tages backup

Action: System couldn't put store on the maintenance mode
Handling: Systemet kunne ikke sætte forretningen i vedligeholdelsestilstand

Action: The database and media backup has been created.
The database backup has been created.
The file was compressed with Zlib, but this extension is not installed on server.
Handling: Filen er komprimeret med Zlib, men dette modul er ikke installeret på serveren.

Action: Unable to create backup. Please, try again later.
Handling: Kan ikke lave backup. Prøv igen senere.

Action: Unable to save the cron expression.
Wrong order of creation for new backup.
You do not have sufficient permissions to enable Maintenance Mode during this operation.
Handling: Du har ikke tilstrækkelige tilladelser til at aktivere vedligeholdelsestilstand.
